1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:04,800
What if I told you seagrass meadows are vital yet often overlooked?

2
00:00:04,800 --> 00:00:09,600
These underwater gardens cover vast areas, providing homes for countless marine species.

3
00:00:09,600 --> 00:00:12,400
But they do more than house fish.

4
00:00:12,400 --> 00:00:14,800
They capture carbon—helping fight climate change.

5
00:00:14,800 --> 00:00:20,400
Studies show they can store up to 83 million tons of carbon yearly, but...

6
00:00:20,400 --> 00:00:24,000
They’re declining rapidly due to pollution and coastal development.

7
00:00:24,000 --> 00:00:25,600
What can we do?

8
00:00:25,600 --> 00:00:26,800
Join the fight!

9
00:00:26,800 --> 00:00:28,000
Support seagrass conservation.

10
00:00:28,000 --> 00:00:29,200
Your actions matter.
